				h1.ar-heading.wf-bg.f-oku.wtxt what is Wayfarer's skill?
				.col-md-6
					p.ar-text With the ability to manipulate the electromagnetic spectrum, Wayfarer is a powerful cosmic entity with control over heat, light and sound. Thrumming with the vibrations of the universe, Wayfarer's REVERB skill represents his ability to master the electromagnetic spectrum. 
					p.ar-text So how does Reverb work? Reverb allows you to swap your discard pile and deck - potentially gaining enormous amounts of life and gaining access to previously-played cards! This ability comes with a built-in cost - you must first trash the top 3 cards of your discard pile. That means the more often you Reverb, the smaller your deck becomes.
					p.ar-text Included below are a couple of examples on how to use this skill!		
