				h1.ar-heading.wf-bg.f-oku.wtxt in conclusion...
				p.ar-text Managing your deck, discard pile, hand and trash all at the same time makes playing Wayfarer intimidating. Learning how to get the most out of your Reverbs and reward cards is not an easy skill and changes wildly depending on your opponent! Surviving into the late game grants careful players with powerful game-ending abilities, so don't be afraid to play it safe. Feeling lost in the vastness of space? Using reverb lets you replay cards that were sitting in our discard pile, so make sure you are trashing stuff you don't want to draw! Given enough time, a clever Wayfarer will win a late-game standoff with any competitor.

